      "date": "2013-09-06 02:23:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n+ HSM subdirectory is visible, even when HSM control is off.\n\n[root@m64-1 ~]# cat /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/scratch-MDT0000/hsm_control \nstopped\n[root@m64-1 ~]# ls /proc/fs/lustre/mdt/scratch-MDT0000/hsm/\nagent_actions  default_archive_id  loop_period   policy    request_timeout\nagents         grace_delay         max_requests  requests\n\n+ lctl set_param works:\n\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl set_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id=2\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm.default_archive_id=2\n\n- lctl conf_param does not work:\n\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl conf_param scratch-MDT*.mdt.hsm.default_archive_id=2\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm.default_archive_id=1\n\nFrom /var/log/messages:\n\nSep  5 03:33:22 m64-1 kernel: Lustre: Modifying parameter scratch-MDT0000.mdt.hsm.default_archive_id in log scratch-MDT0000\nSep  5 03:33:31 m64-1 kernel: LustreError: 1564:0:(obd_config.c:1591:class_config_llog_handler()) MGC10.37.129.11@tcp: cfg command failed: rc = -38\nSep  5 03:33:31 m64-1 kernel: Lustre:    cmd=cf00f 0:scratch-MDT0000  1:mdt.hsm.default_archive_id=2",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
