      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nFunctionality works as expected. HSM subdirectory structure is visible on MDT mount, even if hsm_control is set to stopped. In addition, parameters can be changed and saved persistently with \"set_param -P\".\n\nset_param -P works when hsm_control == \"stopped\":\n\n[root@m64-1 ~]# df -ht lustre\nFilesystem            Size  Used Avail Use% Mounted on\n/dev/sdb             1008M   35M  923M   4% /lustre/mgs\n/dev/sdc              7.5G  446M  6.6G   7% /lustre/scratch/mdt0\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm_control\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm_control=stopped\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm.default_archive_id=1\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl set_param -P mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id=2\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm.default_archive_id=2\n[root@m64-1 ~]# umount /lustre/scratch/mdt0\n[root@m64-1 ~]# umount /lustre/mgs\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lustre_rmmod \n[root@m64-1 ~]# lsmod | grep lnet\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lsmod | grep lustre\n[root@m64-1 ~]# mount -t lustre /dev/sdb /lustre/mgs\n[root@m64-1 ~]# mount -t lustre /dev/sdc /lustre/scratch/mdt0\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm.default_archive_id=2\n\n\nset_param -P works when hsm_control == \"enabled\":\n\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl set_param -P mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm_control=enabled\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm_control\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm_control=enabled\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm.default_archive_id=2\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl set_param -P mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id=3\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm.default_archive_id=3\n[root@m64-1 ~]# umount /lustre/scratch/mdt0\n[root@m64-1 ~]# umount /lustre/mgs\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lustre_rmmod \n[root@m64-1 ~]# mount -t lustre /dev/sdb /lustre/mgs\n[root@m64-1 ~]# mount -t lustre /dev/sdc /lustre/scratch/mdt0\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm_control\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm_control=enabled\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl get_param mdt.scratch-MDT*.hsm.default_archive_id\nmdt.scratch-MDT0000.hsm.default_archive_id=3\n\n\nconf_param does not work under any circumstances:\n\n[root@m64-1 ~]# lctl conf_param scratch-MDT*.mdt.hsm.default_archive_id=5",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 4
    },
